Class MiniIconButton

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.event.EventTarget, javafx.scene.control.Skinnable

    public class MiniIconButton
extends javafx.scene.control.Button
    The MiniIconButton is an extension of the standard button. It gets a second icon, which can be placed above the normal button. The icon is minified and shown
